<p>The sale of their family home seems to be another nail in the coffin of their marriage.</p>

<p>A source told The Sun website said: 'It seems lockdown was just too much for Alfie and Sarah.</p>

<p>'They have found their relationship increasingly strained and he says they've now made the decision to separate.</p>

<p>'He is a doting dad and wants to keep things amicable for the sake of the kids. But he feels ready to move on.'</p>

<p>Other couples to have split up during lockdown include comedian Harry Enfield, Jesy Nelson of Little Mix and Hollyoaks actor Jennifer Metcalfe.</p>
